window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>We are blood. And so are they....<br> <br> We're finally free—and we intend to stay that way. But our most dangerous enemy has plans that could upend the entire world.<br> <br> To carry out those plans, he's making more like us. More people twisted into something monstrous and forced to serve his psychotic ends.<br> <br> My guys and I have to stop him. It's our only hope of getting the peace we've dreamed of—for us and everyone else we've come to care about.<br> <br> But how can we even fight when the foes standing in our way are shadowbloods just like us?</p> <p><i>Fearsome Dream</i> is the final book in Shadowblood Souls, an urban fantasy series for those who love savagely possessive men and fierce heroines who'll fight for what's theirs.</p>"; 
